title: Andres Borregales ready to make own Adam Vinatieri-like Super Bowl 2026 impact for Patriots

sources.name: Yahoo Sports NFL
sources.title: Andres Borregales ready to make own Adam Vinatieri-like Super Bowl 2026 impact for Patriots
sources.description: Now he is the one in Vinatieri’s old cleats — metaphorically speaking — as the kicker for the Patriots in Super Bowl 2026 against the Seahawks.
